ale was distributed to the shareholders in the form of a one time special dividendcitation needed part of the companys louisville complex in  the company acquired the chambord liqueur brand a superpremium black raspberry liqueur produced in france for us  million in  the company acquired tequila herradura a mexican company that produces the casa herradura tequila brand a superpremium tequila produced in mexico for us  million while it also sold its hartman luggage division one of the leaders in the travel goods industry and originally a subdivision of lenox to clarion capitol partners one year later it sold the bolla and fontana candida italian wine brands to gruppo italiano vini giv the terms of neither sale were disclosedcitation needed in  the company sold fetzer vineyards and associated brands to the chilean wine producer viña concha y toro sa for us  million in  the company joined leading alcohol producers as part of a producers commitments to reducing harmful drinking in  the southern comfort and tuaca brands were sold to sazerac company for  million in  brownforman also reached an agreement to purchase the benriach distillery company limited for approximately £ million the purchase brought glendronach benriach and glenglassaugh to brownformans portfolio the company is a sponsor of the brownforman retailer of the year awards given by the american beverage licensees stock informationedit brown forman has two classes of common stock both of which are traded publicly on the new york stock exchange the class a shares carry voting privileges and are thinly traded due to control by the brown family while the class b shares are nonvoting stock china bribery accusationsedit in  brownforman was accused of illegally subsidizing its distributors in china and subsequently delaying payment to them as agreed under contract the shanghai administration for industry and commerce fined brownforman  million renminbi us for illegal subsidization environmental track recordedit this section needs expansion you can help by adding to it november  in  newsweek magazine ranked brownforman in their green rankings which examines  of the largest corporations on their environmental track record brownforman was ranked rd out of  overall and was ranked rd in their industry brandsedit whiskey us woodford reserve kentucky straight bourbon whiskey early times kentucky whiskey jack daniels tennessee whiskey old forester kentucky straight bourbon whiskey the first bottled bourbon sold exclusively in sealed bottles and the oldest bourbon continuously on the market – first bottled in  whisky scotland and canada canadian mist blended canadian whisky collingwood canadian whisky glendronach single malt scotch whisky benriach single malt scotch whisky glenglassaugh single malt scotch whisky wine korbel champagne distributed sonomacutrer wines vodka finlandia maximus vodka little black dress low abv vodka drink tequila pepe lopez tequilas tequila herradura don eduardo tequilas el jimador liqueur chambord raspberry liqueur tuaca italian vanilla liqueur sold  see alsoedit list of major employers in louisville kentucky referencesedit  a b c d e f brownforman corp bfbnyq financials financial times retrieved january     investors brownforman retrieved january     george garvin brown iv a family man rides the bourbon boom theglobeandmailcom may   retrieved november     americas richest families list  brownforman adds chambord to liquor cabinet new york times dealbook march    brownforman completes chambord acquisition press release june    chris mercer november   us casa herradura helps offset costs for brownforman q beverage news  comment justdrinkscom retrieved july     concha y toro buying fetzer for  million wine spectator retrieved december     southern comfort brand sold for m the telegraph january   retrieved december     brownforman to acquire the glendronach benriach and glenglassaugh single malt scotch whiskies retrieved july     brownforman retailers of the y