nforman corporation is one of the largest americanowned companies in the spirits and wine businesscitation needed based in louisville kentucky it manufactures several well known brands throughout the world including jack daniels early times old forester woodford reserve canadian mist glendronach benriach glenglassaugh finlandia herradura korbel and chambord brownforman formerly owned southern comfort and tuaca before selling them off in  as of fiscal  the company had sales of  billion the roughly  members of the brown family cousins that are descendants of founder george garvin brown control more than  of the voting shares and have a net worth of  billion contents  history  stock information  china bribery accusations  environmental track record  brands  see also  references  external links historyedit this section needs expansion with history between  and  you can help by adding to it march  the company was founded in  by george garvin brown a young pharmaceuticals salesman in louisville who had the thennovel idea of selling topgrade whiskey in sealed glass bottles in  the company sold its lenox division one of the oldest and most famous manufacturers of fine china in the united states which had been acquired in  to department  for usd  million the income generated by the sale was distributed to the shareholders in the form of a one time special dividendcitation needed part of the companys louisville complex in  the company acquired the chambord liqueur brand a superpremium black raspberry liqueur produced in france for us  million in  the company acquired tequila herradura a mexican company that produces the casa herradura tequila brand a superpremium tequila produced in mexico for us  million while it also sold its hartman luggage division one of the leaders in the travel goods industry and originally a subdivision of lenox to clarion capitol partners one year later it sold the bolla and fontana candida italian wine brands to gruppo italiano vini giv the terms of neither sale were disclosedcitation needed in  the company sold fetzer vineyards and associated brands to the chilean wine producer viña concha y toro sa for us  million in  the company joined leading alcohol producers as part of a producers commitments to reducing harmful drinking in  the southern comfort and tuaca brands were sold to sazerac company for  million in  brownforman also reached an agreement to purchase the benriach distillery company limited for approximately £ million the purchase brought glendronach benriach and glenglassaugh to brownformans portfolio the company is a sponsor of the brownforman retailer of the year awards given by the american beverage licensees stock informationedit brown forman has two classes of common stock both of which are traded publicly on the new york stock exchange the class a shares carry voting privileges and are thinly traded due to control by the brown family while the class b shares are nonvoting stock china bribery accusationsedit in  brownforman was accused of illegally subsidizing its distributors in china and subsequently delaying payment to them as agreed under contract the shanghai administration for industry and commerce fined brownforman  million renminbi us for illegal subsidization environmental track recordedit this section needs expansion you can help by adding to it november  in  newsweek magazine ranked brownforman in their green rankings which examines  of the largest corporations on their environmental track record brownforman was ranked rd out of  overall and was ranked rd in their industry brandsedit whiskey us woodford reserve kentucky straight bourbon whiskey early times kentucky whiskey jack daniels tennessee whiskey old forester kentucky straight bourbon whiskey the first bottled bourbon sold exclusively in sealed bottles and the oldest bourbon continuously on the market – first bottled in  whisky scotland and canada canadian mist blended canadian whisky collingwood canadian whisky glendronach s